	<name>Bazzite Media Writer</name>
	<summary>A tool to create a live USB drive with an edition of Bazzite</summary>
	<description>
		<p>A tool to create a bootable live USB drive with an edition of Bazzite. Not only can Bazzite Media Writer write an image to your flash drive, it can also download it for you. It offers official Bazzite editions optimized for gaming and desktop use. It provides basic information about each edition to help you make the right choice.</p>
		<p>Bazzite Media Writer can also write other bootable ISOs loaded from your local disk, but keep in mind that it's primarily designed for Bazzite images.</p>
	</description>
